  "properties": {
    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Evaluate Data Questions with AI\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to check if your question meets the RSAIR criteria and get suggestions to improve it.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n**Do This:**\r\n\r\n1. Upload a **PDF file** of the RSAIR criteria from the library.\r\n2. Paste your question into AI Chat. Then ask:\r\n   - *Does this meet the RSAIR criteria? If not, how could I improve it?*\r\n   - *What assumptions am I making in this question?* \r\n3. Review the feedback. Then ask:\r\n   - *Can you help me revise this question to be more [specific/actionable/respectful]?*\r\n4. Copy the revised version and summarize what you changed.",
